        <p style="margin-top:1rem;"><strong>Cancellation policy:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Monthly plans:</strong> Cancel anytime with 30 days written notice. No refund for the current billing month.</li>
          <li><strong>Quarterly plans:</strong> No refund after the first 14 calendar days of the billing period.</li>
          <li><strong>Annual plans:</strong> No refund after the first 30 calendar days of the billing period.</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;">All cancellation requests must be submitted in writing via email to jake@jakefixestech.com. Cancellation is not effective until confirmed in writing by Jake Fixes Tech LLC. Upon cancellation, the client retains full ownership of their website and Jake Fixes Tech LLC will cease management activities at the end of the final paid period.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="terms-section">
        <h2>20. Limitation of Liability — Web Services</h2>
        <p>Jake Fixes Tech LLC is not liable for any loss of business, revenue, data, traffic, search rankings or reputation arising from website downtime, errors, bugs, performance issues or third-party service outages. Our total liability for any web services claim shall not exceed the total amount paid by the client for the specific project or billing period giving rise to the claim.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;">Jake Fixes Tech LLC is not responsible for outages or disruptions caused by Cloudflare, domain registrars, payment processors or any other third-party service. We are not liable for any loss resulting from a client's failure to renew their domain or maintain their own account credentials.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="terms-section">
        <h2>21. Accessibility Compliance</h2>
        <p>Jake Fixes Tech LLC builds all new websites to meet <strong>WCAG 2.1 Level AA</strong> accessibility standards at the time of delivery. Accessibility services apply exclusively to websites built from scratch by Jake Fixes Tech LLC and do not include remediation, auditing or retrofitting of pre-existing websites built by other parties.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;">Compliance is verified at delivery using the WAVE accessibility evaluation tool and manual testing. A passing accessibility report will be provided with Professional and Premium package deliveries.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;"><strong>Post-delivery responsibility:</strong> Jake Fixes Tech LLC is not responsible for maintaining accessibility compliance on content added or modified by the client after delivery. This includes images without alt text, low-contrast color changes, third-party embeds or any structural modifications made outside a Jake Fixes Tech LLC management plan.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;"><strong>ADA Accessibility Recommendation Waiver:</strong> If a client requests content or design choices that do not meet WCAG AA standards, Jake Fixes Tech LLC will inform the client in writing and recommend correction. If the client elects to proceed despite this recommendation, they must sign a separate <strong>ADA Accessibility Recommendation Waiver</strong> before work continues. This waiver documents that Jake Fixes Tech LLC identified and disclosed the accessibility concern and that the client accepted full liability for any resulting legal claims, fines or regulatory action. Jake Fixes Tech LLC is not liable for any ADA-related legal claims arising from client-directed non-compliant design choices.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- GENERAL -->
      <div class="terms-section">
        <h2 style="font-size:1.5rem;color:#2563eb;border-bottom:2px solid #dbeafe;padding-bottom:0.5rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">General Provisions</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="terms-section">
        <h2>22. Force Majeure</h2>
        <p>Jake Fixes Tech LLC is not liable for any failure or delay in performance caused by circumstances beyond our reasonable control, including but not limited to natural disasters, power outages, supplier failures, illness, government orders, pandemics or any other event outside our control ("force majeure event"). In the event of a force majeure event, Jake Fixes Tech LLC will notify you as soon as reasonably practicable and will resume performance when circumstances permit.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="terms-section">
        <h2>23. Governing Law & Dispute Resolution</h2>
        <p>This Agreement shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the <strong>State of New Hampshire</strong>, without regard to its conflict of law provisions. Any disputes arising out of or relating to this Agreement that cannot be resolved informally shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts located in <strong>Grafton County, New Hampshire</strong>.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;">Before pursuing any formal legal action, both parties agree to make a good-faith effort to resolve the dispute directly. You agree to contact Jake Fixes Tech LLC at jake@jakefixestech.com before initiating any legal proceeding.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;">Any claim arising out of or related to this Agreement must be brought within <strong>one (1) year</strong> of the date the claim arose or it shall be permanently barred.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="terms-section">
        <h2>24. Severability</h2>
        <p>If any provision of this Agreement is found to be invalid, illegal or unenforceable by a court of competent jurisdiction, that provision shall be modified to the minimum extent necessary to make it enforceable, and the remaining provisions shall continue in full force and effect.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="terms-section">
        <h2>25. Entire Agreement</h2>
        <p>This Agreement constitutes the entire agreement between you and Jake Fixes Tech LLC with respect to the subject matter herein and supersedes all prior or contemporaneous communications, representations or agreements, whether written or oral. Any modification to this Agreement must be made in writing and acknowledged by Jake Fixes Tech LLC.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="terms-section">
        <h2>26. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>Jake Fixes Tech LLC reserves the right to update these Terms and Conditions at any time. Updated terms will be posted on this page with a revised date. Continued use of our services after the posting of changes constitutes your acceptance of the revised terms. For significant changes, we will make reasonable efforts to notify active clients.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="terms-section">
        <h2>27. Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about these Terms and Conditions, please contact us:</p>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;"><strong>Jake Fixes Tech LLC</strong><br/>
        Littleton, NH<br/>
        Phone: (802) 234-1552<br/>
        Email: jake@jakefixestech.com</p>
      </div>

    </div>
